						`OpenCode is not running at ${probeUrl} and the "opencode" ` +
							"binary was not found on PATH.\n" +
							"Install OpenCode first: https://opencode.ai\n" +
							`Or start it manually: opencode serve --port ${DEFAULT_OPENCODE_PORT}`,
					);
